","url":"/concepts/ci#failure-vocabulary","content":"See the CI setup guide for GitHub App registration, `.runyard/ci.yml` reference, runner setup, and troubleshooting."},"318":{"id":"/concepts/deep-links","page_id":"/concepts/deep-links","type":"page","content":"Deep Links","breadcrumbs":["Docs","Concepts"],"tags":[],"url":"/concepts/deep-links"},"319":{"id":"/concepts/deep-links-0","page_id":"/concepts/deep-links","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/concepts/deep-links","content":"Every Hub URL is shareable - the hash-route grammar of the web app and the deep links the API returns."},"320":{"id":"/concepts/deep-links-1","page_id":"/concepts/deep-links","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/concepts/deep-links#route-grammar","content":"Route grammar"},"321":{"id":"/concepts/deep-links-2","page_id":"/concepts/deep-links","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/concepts/deep-links#deep-links-in-api-payloads","content":"Deep links in API payloads"},"322":{"id":"/concepts/deep-links-3","page_id":"/concepts/deep-links","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/concepts/deep-links","content":"Every URL in the Runyard web app is shareable: the app is a hash-routed SPA, so any view — a run's logs, a workflow's graph, a pending approval — can be copied from the address bar and opened by anyone with access to the Hub. Links have the form:"},"323":{"id":"/concepts/deep-links-4","page_id":"/concepts/deep-links","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/concepts/deep-links#route-grammar","content":"Route"},"324":{"id":"/concepts/deep-links-5","page_id":"/concepts/deep-links","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/concepts/deep-links#route-grammar","content":"View"},"325":{"id":"/concepts/deep-links-6","page_id":"/concepts/deep-links","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/concepts/deep-links#route-grammar","content":"`#runs`"},"326":{"id":"/concepts/deep-links-7","page_id":"/concepts/deep-links","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/concepts/deep-links#route-grammar","content":"Run list (also the home view)."},"327":{"id":"/conc